0-09-04T03:02:52.000Z","msg":"利多於弊？"},{"pid":"820adbca5f228fdb080674b088096f66dd74e97e","tid":2187925,"uid":47239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T03:03:07.000Z","msg":"2011年，Google計劃在香港設立數據中心，當時港府表示歡迎。然而，舉行動土儀式後，相關地段卻荒蕪兩年，2013年，Google宣布放棄計劃。官方解釋，原因是香港缺乏可擴展的土地以應對急速發展。同年，Google啟用在台灣興建的數據中心。<br />\n<br />\n當時有人推測，Google放棄駐港與政治因素有關，由於Google於2010年將業務撤出內地，故駐港的計劃受到阻撓。然而，如果港府真的要「從中作梗」，2011年根本不會批地予Google。較為合理的推測，似乎是香港能源政策、人才配套、土地資源的各種不足，令Google撤回計劃。而香港再生能源發展滯後，或是箇中關鍵。<br />\n<br />\n人哋好耐之前已經放棄係香港起data centre啦<br />\n地又貴，又無再生能源發電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c5f89607a474cc3b7051f27618e392df3ea406","tid":2187925,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c0460821f660bfac4efb3ea3233ae0b0bdb5122","tid":2187925,"uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T02:44:48.000Z","msg":"唔係社會穩定，有利營商環境咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T03:32:00.000Z","msg":"令到外國勢力自動離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n期待幾時演變返用銀號<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d30b9850480d4126002b9e9b4aba5fdad6508a6","tid":2187925,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T03:38:00.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"761f63e15d051a002c188faa1bbe1cf9b8423e93","tid":2187925,"uid":39777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c0460821f660bfac4efb3ea3233ae0b0bdb5122","tid":2187925,"uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T02:44:48.000Z","msg":"唔係社會穩定，有利營商環境咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T03:39:13.000Z","msg":"好穩定喎，無哂外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":